snippet.title: The Harlem Shake vs Gangnam Style Dance Game
snippet.description:
AWESOME NEW FREE GAME NOW AVAILABLE ON iOS & ANDROID!

Download it for iPhone & iPad here:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/harlem-shake-vs-gangnam-style/id617914813?ls=1&mt=8

Android version here: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dragongamestudio.harlemgangnam

♫ ♫ ♫  What's  your favorite move: The Harlem Shake or Gangnam Style? ♫ ♫ ♫ Play as either one in this epic dance game! The biggest YouTube legends ever battling it out. Have you got what it takes to tap with the best?!

Do you prefer Harlem Shake or Oppa Gangnam Style?! In this game it doesn't matter, you can choose to play as either one. This is more fun than a night out at the club!

It's fast, it's fun, it's exciting:

★ Simple but powerful controls
★ Amazing HD Retina graphics
★ High Quality music
★ Ultimate Sound effects
★ Awesome Rhythm
★ Play as Harlem Shaker
★ Play as PSY Gangnam
★ Battle with your Game Center friends
★ Mega Combo system

+ MUCH more fun ACTION!

Get ready to TAP your night away to the amazing tunes of The Harlem Shake or Oppa Gangnam Style. This great game will surprise you, entertain you & WOW you!! Download it now to shake it with the best.... 

COMING SOON to iPhone, iPad, iPod & all Android devices!

For more informations and screenshots:

http://www.dragongamestudio.com/the-harlem-shake-vs-gangnam-style-dance-game/

PSY really is a gentleman!
